WEBVTT

00:10:57.063 --> 00:11:00.134
"Biodiversity underpins life on earth."

00:11:00.158 --> 00:11:03.299
And if we don't look after
this biodiversity,

00:11:03.323 --> 00:11:04.795
if we don't protect it,

00:11:04.819 --> 00:11:08.336
if we don't actually
harness it in the right way,

00:11:08.360 --> 00:11:12.154
we are threatening
our own livelihoods on this planet.

00:11:12.178 --> 00:11:16.847
When we talk about the contribution
from countries of the north

00:11:16.871 --> 00:11:20.427
to the Green Fund
for the protection of our planet,

00:11:20.451 --> 00:11:22.108
it is not charity.

00:11:22.544 --> 00:11:27.540
It is to ensure our own collective
livelihoods on this planet.

00:11:27.564 --> 00:11:29.667
So this is something
that must be addressed.

